name: Verify that user is able to see output for valid python code
fullName: Graph Page Features: Verify that user is able to see output for valid python code

steps.name: Given  The user is on home page of ds portal
When  The user clicks Sign in link for ds and enters valid credentials
Then  The user lands on the graph page on clicking Get started button for graph module
Given  The user is on the tryEditor page after clicking Try here button in Inside Graph
When  The user writes valid Python code in the editor of Inside Graph page and clicks Run button from sheetname "tryEditorCode" and row 0
Then  The user should be able to see output in the console for Inside Graph
